The performance metrics of all the low-level methods, as well as their combinations with high-level methods, are given in Supplementary Tables S3-S9. It is worth pointing out that a recent study by Tabor et al.27 also considered DFT and SEQM based methods for performing a similar calibration exercise to determine an optimum method for predicting redox potentials of 28 quinone molecules using ΔErxn\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
